msgstr "Haslo administratora Poweradmin"

#: install/templates/step3.html.twig:107
msgid "Provide a password"
msgstr "Podaj hasło"

#: install/templates/step3.html.twig:111
msgid ""
"The password of the Poweradmin administrator. This administrator has full "
"rights to Poweradmin using the web interface."
msgstr ""
"Haslo administratora Poweradmin. Ten administrator ma pelne uprawnienia do Poweradmin za posrednictwem interfejsu webowego."

#: install/templates/step3.html.twig:112
msgid ""
"Password must be at least 6 characters long, contain at least one uppercase "
"letter, one lowercase letter, and one number."
msgstr ""
"Haslo musi miec co najmniej 6 znakow i zawierac co najmniej jedna wielka litere, jedna mala litere i jedna cyfre."

